276
00:13:51,539 --> 00:13:53,207
[sighs] Damn it.

277
00:13:59,672 --> 00:14:02,675
-They're suing you?
-This chick is claiming she has whiplash.

278
00:14:02,758 --> 00:14:05,177
She wasn't in the car when I hit it.

279
00:14:05,261 --> 00:14:08,889
This is on you. You should've pretended
you didn't see it and walked away.

280
00:14:08,973 --> 00:14:10,724
Like everyone else does.

281
00:14:10,808 --> 00:14:14,019
