and never said anything.

282
00:14:14,103 --> 00:14:16,105
But I'm trying to be good.

283
00:14:16,188 --> 00:14:17,898
[laughing]

284
00:14:17,982 --> 00:14:20,359
How is that working out for you?

285
00:14:22,778 --> 00:14:24,238
[machines clacking]

286
00:14:28,033 --> 00:14:29,493
