287
00:14:29,577 --> 00:14:31,161
{\an8}It's open, dummy!

288
00:14:32,663 --> 00:14:34,373
Eleanor, where have you been?

289
00:14:34,456 --> 00:14:39,086
Oh, hey, man. Sorry,
it's been a crazy month, you know?

290
00:14:39,169 --> 00:14:41,380
